brokers in 1979 and likely candidates for a coterie closeknit and 
powerful enough to make such a drastic decision 
brezhnev then 73 held the top positions in both the government 
and the communist party president and party general secretary 
gromyko then 70 had ruled the foreign ministry for 22 years 
gen ustinov then 71 was both minister of defense and marshal 
